<h1> Hello <%= @author.first_name %>!</h1>
<p>Someone has activated the password reset procedure for your account on Blog</p>
<p>You can change the password by clicking on this link:</p>
<h3><%= edit_pass_reset_url(@author.confirm_token) %></h3>
<p>If you have received a few letters about password recovery, then you must go to the password reset page using the link from the most recent letter.</p>
<p>If you did not request a password reset, just ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your password will not be changed until you click on the link above.</p>
